      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节主题产品页</title>\n<style>\n  body {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    background-color: #F4F4F5;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    color: #333;\n  }\n  header, section, nav {\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    max-width: 800px;\n  }\n  h1, h2 {\n    color: #D32F2F;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n  p {\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  #product-banner {\n    background-color: #FFD54F;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 40px 20px;\n    border-bottom: 4px solid #D32F2F;\n  }\n  #product-info {\n    background-color: #fff;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n  #price-block {\n    background-color: #fff;\n    border: 2px solid #D32F2F;\n    padding: 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n  #promotion-tools {\n    background-color: #fff8e1;\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    border: 1px solid #FFD54F;\n  }\n  #promotion-tools div {\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel {\n    background-color: #fff;\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel button {\n    background-color: #D32F2F;\n    color: white;\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    border: none;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel button:hover {\n    background-color: #b71c1c;\n  }\n  #cart-management {\n    background-color: #fff;\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n  #category-nav {\n    background-color: #D32F2F;\n    color: white;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n  #category-nav ul {\n    list-style: none;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    display: flex;\n  }\n  #category-nav li {\n    padding: 10px 15px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n  }\n  #category-nav li:hover {\n    background-color: #b71c1c;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<section id=\"product-banner\">\n  <h1>欢庆春节礼盒</h1>\n  <p>以喜庆红金配色呈现节日氛围，融合品牌传承与品质升级，带来新年的美好祝愿。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"product-info\">\n  <h2>礼盒规格与组合</h2>\n  <p>包含多款精选年货零食，礼盒包装精美，适合送礼与自用。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"price-block\">\n  <h2>现价 ￥199 原价 ￥299</h2>\n  <p>限时优惠立减 ￥100</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"promotion-tools\">\n  <div>限时倒计时：00:12:45</div>\n  <div>领取满200减50优惠券</div>\n  <div>库存紧张，仅剩 20 件</div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"purchase-channel\">\n  <button>立即购买</button>\n  <div>\n    数量：\n    <select>\n      <option>1</option>\n      <option>2</option>\n      <option>3</option>\n    </select>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"cart-management\">\n  <h2>购物车</h2>\n  <div>商品列表：礼盒 A、礼盒 B</div>\n  <div>数量调整与删除操作</div>\n</section>\n\n<nav id=\"category-nav\">\n  <ul>\n    <li>坚果类</li>\n    <li>糖果类</li>\n    <li>干果类</li>\n    <li>其他年货</li>\n  </ul>\n</nav>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
